 \"We learned a lot from them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2748, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"State forecaster Meteo France announced a high temperature of 37 degrees Celsius (98.6\\u00b0F) in Paris, which led to heat protocols in some events.\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2767, \"end\": 2779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9t\\u00e9o-France\", \"score\": 0.9999999998472049, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Meteo France\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9t\\u00e9o-France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9t\\u00e9o-France\"}, {\"begin\": 2843, \"end\": 2848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999858232514, \"rank\": 1.417661271324159e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Football players were allowed water breaks, tennis players could use additional breaks to take a shower, BMX riders sat under umbrellas between runs and horses were monitored with thermal cameras.\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 3091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3000, \"end\": 3003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.7489863324024072, \"rank\": 0.19452330624706388, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3137, \"entities\": []}]}"